							<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
								During our launch period, we offer lifetime access to Zeyn for a one-time payment. This means you will retain access to the Service for as long as we continue to operate it, without additional subscription fees.
							</p>
						</section>
						
						<section>
							<h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Termination</h2>
							<p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
								We may terminate or suspend access to our Service immediately, without prior notice or liability, for any reason whatsoever, including without limitation if you breach the Terms.
